	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, looking at that image and at my TV (I know this is not a relevant point since all TVs vary), some of those are similar but obviously a few differences are there.
<br />
<br />For instance, $15 and $16 look pretty similar on mine.  The $X8 have a little more greenish tint to them, but not as much as the $X9 ones.
<br />
<br />But $2D and $3D were definitely not black.
<br />
<br />For emulators, I use the ascquire.pal I found at some site, which is fairly good.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


