	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The first Garage Cart used the $0D color in it somewhere, probably in the intro (based on an old palette file that I neglected to change).  But just out of the first (maybe 10?) carts there was one person's TV it messed up on.  So the later ones are a revision with those palette bytes changed.
<br />
<br />I don't know about the other xD colors, but 0D is one to avoid.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


